{"tid":2411623,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"Angelababy 英文藝名遭內地作家追擊 陶傑建議：改成「安琪拉嬰兒」","createTime":"2021-02-17T12:43:55.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-17T15:20:47.000Z","uid":66271,"like":25,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"9f32e6ab57107542df570136d3dd05a5195cc994","tid":2411623,"uid":66271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T12:43:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/HhbNl3bxEOCmp7zrigjePA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTY0MDtoPTY0MA--/https://s.yimg.com/uu/api/res/1.2/vmJIvu3.VLwEyWq3FNZmfA--~B/aD02NDA7dz02NDA7YXBwaWQ9eXRhY2h5b24-/https://media.zenfs.com/zh-tw/entertainment.nownews.hk/68809ca0e82b29c4a335456d667cd785\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FHhbNl3bxEOCmp7zrigjePA--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTY0MDtoPTY0MA--%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fuu%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FvmJIvu3.VLwEyWq3FNZmfA--~B%2FaD02NDA7dz02NDA7YXBwaWQ9eXRhY2h5b24-%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-tw%2Fentertainment.nownews.hk%2F68809ca0e82b29c4a335456d667cd785&h=a6e3175e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n楊穎一直以 Angelababy 的名字在娛樂圈發展。日前，有「悲情詩人」之稱，兼自稱為「第 7 代導演」的內地導演劉信達，就在微博針對楊穎發文，批評她以英文名在內地發展。而陶傑亦很快抽水，出手幫她改名做「安琪拉嬰兒」。<br />\n<br />\n劉信達發文，指內地人對外國的節日及洋化覺得反感，希望 Angelababy 改用中文藝名。他表示：「西方人對應的是東方人，而不是南方人，不要無知者無畏，不要無聊當有趣！」更指 Baby 應該自己選擇引退。<br />\n<br />\n很快，陶傑亦在 Facebook 出帖幫忙「解釋」，指她用英文名並非祟洋，而是鼓勵下一代學好英文。他又指出 Maggie Q、Lisa S 亦有中國或亞裔血統，但廣電局並未要求她們用中文名。不過他就樂意為 Angelababy 改名，分別有「安琪拉嬰兒」、「安琪拉貝比」以及「安琪拉悲 B」。不知網民心水又是哪一個？"},{"pid":"3e06a43a431227ccb4b6929e7c47fb19a0905dd1","tid":2411623,"uid":38646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T13:44:29.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">你</span></span>"},{"pid":"ffb673df3f1cf3592cc7cc9dda47fa157e9f969a","tid":2411623,"uid":17641,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T13:47:26.000Z","msg":"安琪拉牛B<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02